{"type": "assistant", "message": {"id": "msg_1783430186227", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "paper-wiki 中没有任何关于歌词/语义同质化/文化趋势分析的论文记录。OMC Wiki MCP 工具（`wiki_query` / `wiki_ingest`）**不在当前可用工具集中** —— ToolSearch 搜索返回\"No matching deferred tools\"，这意味着 `wiki_query` 在本进程不可用。我必须按 skill 要求用 `free-search` 补充。"}], "model": "GLM-5.2-w4a8", "stop_reason": null, "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 0, "output_tokens": 0, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}, "context_management": null}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "7adfc9b8-6936-46dd-9c20-5108afde690a", "uuid": "b1017e20-0a97-484c-8e9d-430cc5a0e6a5"}
